Ngeneric:Invisible-Pin|pin@673||-76|-214.5|||||SIM_spice_card(D5G1;)S[* 4-Bit Full Adder - Worst-Case Critical Path Testbench,* Power Supply,vdd vdd 0 DC 3,* Tie A inputs HIGH (3V),vA1 A1 0 DC 3,vA2 A2 0 DC 3,vA3 A3 0 DC 3,vA4 A4 0 DC 3,* Tie B inputs LOW (0V),vB1 B1 0 DC 0,vB2 B2 0 DC 0,vB3 B3 0 DC 0,vB4 B4 0 DC 0,* Toggle Cin to trigger the carry ripple,"* Pulses from 0V to 3V, delayed by 2ns, 10ns width",vCin Cin 0 PULSE (0 3 2ns 0.001ns 0.001ns 10ns 20ns),* Short Transient Analysis (Only need enough time for one full cycle),.tran 0 30ns,* Library Include,".include C:\\Users\\enslenc1\\Documents\\GitHub\\VLSI\\ElectricVLSI\\TransistorSpecs\\tsmc018.lib",* --- WORST-CASE TIMING MEASUREMENTS ---,* Measure Low-to-High Propagation Delay (Cin rising edge to Cout rising edge),.meas TRAN tpd_lh TRIG v(Cin) VAL=1.5 RISE=1 TARG v(cout) VAL=1.5 RISE=1,* Measure High-to-Low Propagation Delay (Cin falling edge to Cout falling edge),.meas TRAN tpd_hl TRIG v(Cin) VAL=1.5 FALL=1 TARG v(cout) VAL=1.5 FALL=1,* Calculate Average Worst-Case Propagation Delay,.meas TRAN tpd_avg PARAM='(tpd_lh + tpd_hl) / 2']
